<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَأَلَّفَ بَرْقُ الْحَقِّ في الْعَارِضِ النَّجْدِي ... فَعَمَّ جَمِيعَ الكَوْنِ في الغَوْرِ والنَّجْدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>به زُعْزُعَتْ أَرْكَانُ كِسْرَى وقَيْصَرٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ولم يُجَد مَا حَازَا مِنْ الْمَالِ والجُنْدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَأَمْثَالُهَا في السَّالِكينَ طرَيِقَهَمْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَرنَاَ كَمَا قَدْ قَالَهُ صَادِقُ الوَعْدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَلِلهِ حَمْدٌ يَرْتَضِيهِ لِنَفْسِهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عَلَى نِعْمٍ زَادَتْ عَنْ الحَصْرِ والعَدِّ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَأعْظَمهما بَعْثُ الرَّسُولِ مُحَمَّدٍ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَمِينُ إله الحَقِّ وَاسِطَةَ العِقْدِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>دَعَانَا إِلى الإسلامِ دِينِ إِلَهَنَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وتَوْحِيدِهِ بالْقَوْلِ والفِعْلِ والقَصْدِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>هَدَانَا بِهِ بَعْدَ الضَّلالَةِ والعَمَى<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَأَنْقَذَنَا بَعْدَ الغِوَايَةِ بالرُّشْدِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>حَبَانَا وَأَعْطَانَا الذِي فَوْقَ وَهْمِنَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وأَمْكَنَنَا مِن كُلِّ طَاغٍ وَمُعْتَدِّ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَأَيَّدَنَا بالنَّصْرِ واتَّسَعَتْ لَنَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>مَمَالِكُ لا تَدْعُوا سِوَى الوَاحِدِ الفَرْدِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَنَسْأَلُهُ إِتْمَامَ نِعْمَتِهِ بأنْ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>يُثَبِّتَنَا عِنْدَ الْمَصَادِرِ كَالوِرْدِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فيا فوزَ عبدٍ قَاَم لله جاهِدًا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>عَلَى قَدَمِ التجريدِ يَهْدِي وَيَسْتَهْدِي<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>